                 Overview of Office of SWP Planning Activities

Supply Reliability Planning

     * Facility Integrity
     * Ground Water Supply
     * Bay Delta Hearings and Program Development

Delta Planning

     * North, South, and West Delta Facilities

     * Contracts and water rights

     * Other projects that affect the multiple-use Delta water supplies

Modeling Support

     * Development of simulation models of Central Valley hydrology,
       consumptive use, depletions and groundwater
     * Development of statewide simulation models of State Water
       Project-Central Valley Project operations
     * Development of flow and water quality models of the Bay-Delta
       estuary


